                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"><desc type="GuestText">On the recto of the fore guard leaf, there is found the tragic tale of a princess who fell in love with her father's adversary and betrayed her father, who was killed in battle. Her victorious lover married her, but then killed her to avenge her father.</desc><q xml:lang="am"/></item>
